            "type": "text",
            "text": "Chunk Size vs Retrieval Quality"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Chunk size affects both embedding quality and retrieval precision:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "Too small (< 100 tokens): "
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Each chunk lacks enough context for the embedding to capture meaning. A single sentence about \"connection pooling\" could match queries about swimming pools."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "Too large (> 1000 tokens): "
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "The embedding averages over many topics. A chapter-level chunk scores mediocre similarity for most queries even when it contains the answer buried within."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "Sweet spot (200–600 tokens): "
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Enough context for the embedding to be meaningful; small enough that the retrieved chunk is on-topic. For most prose documents, 400 tokens with 64 overlap is a reliable starting point."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
