                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Use a language-aware parser (tree-sitter or ast) to extract function/class bodies. A function body is already the right unit of retrieval."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
